values: So...found my livejournal again! So I decided to bitch and moan to it...but 1st I got some great news. I got a girlfriend!!! Her name is Sara and she's great. I've known her for years, she lives across the street from my Aunt Missys and she comes up to the mountain every weekend with the rest of the people I know. She's awsome, i love it. ;] So about today, such a long day at work. Problems everywhere, problems with the printers, problems with the boxes, problems with the sleeves, problems with the temperature of the egg, problems with the employees that just keep on talking...problems with everything! Got a small headache, my neck is killing me, my arm that sara slept on is killing me (not complaining that she slept on it but that shes not here to rub it -.- ), ate too much candy last night so my jaw is hurting from all that chewing...I'm gonna stop complaining now.

ok well, i didn't post all weekend so imma post today about my weekend. Well saturday was kinda gay but then i was hapy near the end. I sat home 1/2 the day doing nothing then I decided to call Jacqui to see what she was up to. She told me she was going to go shopping and asked me if I wanted to join, of course I said 'yes'. So I went upstairs to put my shoes on and Bill like fucking flipped out on me about not having a job and he swears im not lookin, which is BULLSHIT. So we argued back and forth for a while and he basically told me that I had till October 1st to get a job or im out of the house. Around that time jacqui knocked on the door and came inside to hear the end of the argument. So we went shopping ahd we both had a good time, SHE WANTS JEANS BUT DOESNT LIKE ANY THAT FIT HER!!! Girls are so hard to deal with. ;x just kidding ;] Then we went back to my house and she stayed here for like 10 minutes and left. My rents wernt home when we came to my house so i was happy, so i sat around and chilled. Chris said he was going to come over for a little bit, so he came over for like an hour at the max and he left. So i was again bored so i called mimmo at like 9:30 and said come over we are ordering chinese. So we did just that, and he left at 10:30....AGAIN I WAS BORED! So i sat around and did nothing...called my baby mary ellen and i think i fell asleep on the phone. ok next post is sundays..
